<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Online Store</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 36px;
        }
        nav {
            background-color: #666;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        nav a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        nav a:hover {
            background-color: #999;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-around;
        }
        .product {
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            background-color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            width: calc(33.33% - 20px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        .product:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
        .product img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }
        .product-info {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .product-info h2 {
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .product-info p {
            color: #666;
        }
        .product-info button {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .product-info button:hover {
            background-color: #555;
        }
        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            width: 100%;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>FORD CHEATS</h1>
    </header>
    <nav>
        <a href="#">Home</a>
        <a href="#">Shop</a>
        <a href="#">Contact</a>
    </nav>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="product">
            <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64,">
            <div class="product-info">
                <h2>1 day SKIN CHANGER</h2>
                <p>FN SKIN CHANGER. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.</p>
                <p>£3.50</p>
                <button>Add to Cart</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="product">
            <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64,">
            <div class="product-info">
                <h2>3 day skin changer</h2>
                <p>3 day skin changer. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.</p>
                <p>£5</p>
                <button>Add to Cart</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="product">
            <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64,">
            <div class="product-info">
                <h2>1 week skin changer</h2>
                <p>1 week skin changer. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.</p>
                <p>£15</p>
                <button>Add to Cart</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Add more products as needed -->
        <div class="product">
            <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64,">
            <div class="product-info">
                <h2>1 month SKIN CHANGER</h2>
                <p>FN SKIN CHANGER. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.</p>
                <p>£15</p>
                <button>Add to Cart</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
	<div class="product">
            <img src="https://i.epvpimg.com/sswIgab.png">
            <div class="product-info">
                <h2>1 day soft aim and esp</h2>
                <p>1 day soft aim and esp. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.</p>
                <p>£5</p>
                <button>Add to Cart</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Online Store. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
